{"data":[{"TaskID":1,"TaskName":"Use-Case Diagrams","StartDate":"2026-03-02T16:00:00.000Z","EndDate":"2026-03-07T01:00:00.000Z","Duration":5,"Progress":0,"color":"241","Predecessor":"","resources":[],"info":"<p><br></p>","DurationUnit":"day"},{"TaskID":2,"TaskName":"UML Class Diagrams","StartDate":"2026-03-09T15:00:00.000Z","EndDate":"2026-03-14T00:00:00.000Z","Duration":5,"Progress":0,"color":"211","Predecessor":"1FS","resources":[],"info":"<p><br></p>","DurationUnit":"day"},{"TaskID":3,"TaskName":"UML Sequence Diagram","StartDate":"2026-03-16T15:00:00.000Z","EndDate":"2026-03-21T00:00:00.000Z","Duration":5,"Progress":0,"color":"181","Predecessor":"2FS","resources":[],"info":"<p><br></p>","DurationUnit":"day"},{"TaskID":4,"TaskName":"Design Presentation Prep","StartDate":"2026-03-23T15:00:00.000Z","EndDate":"2026-03-28T00:00:00.000Z","Duration":5,"Progress":0,"color":"151","Predecessor":"3FS","resources":[],"info":"<p><br></p>","DurationUnit":"day"},{"TaskID":5,"TaskName":"Client Module Implementation Initialization","StartDate":"2026-03-30T15:00:00.000Z","EndDate":"2026-04-08T00:00:00.000Z","Duration":7,"Progress":0,"color":"331","Predecessor":"4FS","resources":[{"resourceId":"Darien","resourceName":"Darien","unit":100},{"resourceId":"Victor","resourceName":"Victor","unit":100}],"info":"<p>Implementation Initialization.</p><p>Get the Project Space for the Client Organized.<br>Familiarize with the Git tool, preferably using the CLI.<br>Commit often, push at the end of work sessions. Use branches. Only push to main when ABSOLUTELY sure.<br><br></p><p><br>The deliverable by the end of this week is dependency level classes. Any classes that require other classes' implementation should be done. If there are little or no dependencies produce classes according to the SRS document. Refer to that often.</p><p><br></p><p>Next week will expect full whitebox testing, and at minimum an 90% functional CLI interface with the application.&nbsp;</p>","DurationUnit":"day"},{"TaskID":6,"TaskName":"Server Module Implementation Initialization","StartDate":"2026-03-30T15:00:00.000Z","EndDate":"2026-04-08T00:00:00.000Z","Duration":7,"Progress":0,"color":"271","Predecessor":"4FS","resources":[{"resourceId":"Ola","resourceName":"Ola","unit":100},{"resourceId":"Clarize","resourceName":"Clarize","unit":100}],"info":"<p>Implementation Initialization.</p><p>Get the Project Space for the Server Organized.<br>Familiarize with the Git tool, preferably using the CLI.<br>Commit often, push at the end of work sessions. Use branches. Only push to main when ABSOLUTELY sure.<br><br></p><p><br>The\n deliverable by the end of this week is dependency level classes. Any \nclasses that require other classes' implementation should be done. If \nthere are little or no dependencies produce classes according to the SRS\n document. Refer to that often.</p><p><br></p><p>Next week will expect a full whitebox testable application for all the classes, as well as a 90% complete CLI with the application.</p>","DurationUnit":"day"},{"TaskID":7,"TaskName":"Client Module Implementation","StartDate":"2026-04-08T15:00:00.000Z","EndDate":"2026-04-17T00:00:00.000Z","Duration":7,"Progress":0,"color":"331","Predecessor":"5FS","resources":[{"resourceId":"Darien","resourceName":"Darien","unit":100},{"resourceId":"Victor","resourceName":"Victor","unit":100}],"info":"<p>Functional Application.</p><p>Get the Project Space for the Client Organized.<br>Familiarize with the Git tool, preferably using the CLI.<br>Commit often, push at the end of work sessions. Use branches. Only push to main when ABSOLUTELY sure.</p><p><br></p><p>By this point, the application runs, perhaps missing a few features or logistical errors.&nbsp;</p><p>There should be a driver that contains ALL the white-box testing of the application.&nbsp;</p><p>At minimum there's a CLI with the application to work with.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Next week will expect integration between the Client and the Server. Any bugs, errors, exceptions should be mitigated by that point.</p><p><br></p>","DurationUnit":"day"},{"TaskID":8,"TaskName":"Server Module Implementation","StartDate":"2026-04-08T15:00:00.000Z","EndDate":"2026-04-17T00:00:00.000Z","Duration":7,"Progress":0,"color":"271","Predecessor":"6FS","resources":[{"resourceId":"Ola","resourceName":"Ola","unit":100},{"resourceId":"Clarize","resourceName":"Clarize","unit":100}],"info":"<p>Functional Application.</p><p>Get the Project Space for the Client Organized.<br>Familiarize with the Git tool, preferably using the CLI.<br>Commit often, push at the end of work sessions. Use branches. Only push to main when ABSOLUTELY sure.</p><p><br></p><p>By this point, the application runs, perhaps missing a few features or logistical errors.&nbsp;</p><p>There should be a driver that contains ALL the white-box testing of the application.&nbsp;</p><p>At minimum there's a CLI with the application to work with.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Next week will expect integration between the Client and the Server. Any exceptions, bugs, or errors should be mitigated by that point.&nbsp;<br><br></p><p><br></p>","DurationUnit":"day"},{"TaskID":9,"TaskName":"Client Module Implementation Integration","StartDate":"2026-04-17T15:00:00.000Z","EndDate":"2026-04-28T00:00:00.000Z","Duration":7,"Progress":0,"color":"331","Predecessor":"7FS","resources":[{"resourceId":"Darien","resourceName":"Darien","unit":100},{"resourceId":"Victor","resourceName":"Victor","unit":100}],"info":"<p>Fully Functional Standalone Application.</p><p>Get the Project Space for the Client Organized.<br>Familiarize with the Git tool, preferably using the CLI.<br>Commit often, push at the end of work sessions. Use branches. Only push to main when ABSOLUTELY sure.</p><p><br></p><p>By this point, there are no program crashes, full exception handling, and full whitebox as well as black box testing using a CLI or GUI. The application now must be put together, communicating over a network seamlessly, testing all features.&nbsp;</p><p>Before next time, is to stress test even further than what was done in the whitebox/blackbox, as well as prepare for the Final Presentation. If something breaks, this is the week to debug and fix it.</p><p><br></p>","DurationUnit":"day"},{"TaskID":10,"TaskName":"Server Module Implementation Integration","StartDate":"2026-04-17T15:00:00.000Z","EndDate":"2026-04-28T00:00:00.000Z","Duration":7,"Progress":0,"color":"271","Predecessor":"8FS","resources":[{"resourceId":"Ola","resourceName":"Ola","unit":100},{"resourceId":"Clarize","resourceName":"Clarize","unit":100}],"info":"<p>Fully Functional Standalone Application.</p><p>Get the Project Space for the Client Organized.<br>Familiarize with the Git tool, preferably using the CLI.<br>Commit often, push at the end of work sessions. Use branches. Only push to main when ABSOLUTELY sure.</p><p><br></p><p>By\n this point, there are no program crashes, full exception handling, and \nfull whitebox as well as black box testing using a CLI or GUI. The \napplication now must be put together, communicating over a network \nseamlessly, testing all features.&nbsp;</p><p>Before next time, is to stress \ntest even further than what was done in the whitebox/blackbox, as well \nas prepare for the Final Presentation. If something breaks, this is the \nweek to debug and fix it.</p><p><br><br></p>","DurationUnit":"day"},{"TaskID":11,"TaskName":"Final Presentation Prep","StartDate":"2026-04-28T15:00:00.000Z","EndDate":"2026-05-07T00:00:00.000Z","Duration":7,"Progress":0,"color":"","Predecessor":"10FS","resources":[],"info":"<p><br></p>","DurationUnit":"day"}],"resources":[{"resourceId":"Clarize","resourceName":"Clarize"},{"resourceId":"Darien","resourceName":"Darien"},{"resourceId":"Ola","resourceName":"Ola"},{"resourceId":"Victor","resourceName":"Victor"}],"projectStartDate":null,"projectEndDate":null,"advanced":{"columns":[{"name":"Task ID","width":"70","show":true},{"name":"Task Name","width":"350","show":true},{"name":"Start Date","width":"130","show":false},{"name":"End Date","width":"130","show":false},{"name":"Duration","width":"130","show":false},{"name":"Progress %","width":"150","show":false},{"name":"Dependency","width":"150","show":false},{"name":"Resources","width":"200","show":false},{"name":"Color","width":"100","show":false}],"zoomLevel":0,"timezone":"America/Los_Angeles","timezoneOffset":480,"dependencyConflict":"Add Offset to Dependency","dateFormat":"yyyy-MM-dd","timeFormat":"HH:mm","firstDayOfWeek":0,"workWeek":["Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday"],"workTime":[{"from":8,"to":12},{"from":13,"to":17}],"holidays":[]}}